        <abstract>
            <p>Sends CD some remarks he made before the Academy of Natural Sciences [Philadelphia].</p> 
<p>TM is indebted to the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> for first suggesting to him which observations might be useful to those working out the greater laws of nature.</p> 
        </abstract>
